This interface aims to be as-compatible-as-possible visually and interactivly
with the standard tty interface ... except with tiles ;)

non NetHack/SLASH'EM newt interface Keys:
--------------------------------------------
(ie keyboard commands added by newt)

Alt-Enter : Toggle Fullscreen Mode
F3        : Resize game window to match map size
F4        : Change video mode  
F5|Tab    : Toggle ASCII/Tileset view mode
F6        : Toggle positionbar display method
F8        : Toggle tilset zoom mode
F9        : Zoom Out
F10       : Zoom In
